%section#services_new.services
  %div
    %h3 This authentication is new to Raids Per Loot
    %p.small
      Provider: #{@authhash[:provider]}
      %br/
      ID: #{@authhash[:uid]}
      %br/
      Name: #{@authhash[:name]}
      %br/
      Email: #{@authhash[:email]}
      %br/
    = form_tag :controller => 'services', :action => 'newaccount' do
      = submit_tag 'Confirm and create new account'
      = submit_tag 'Cancel'
  %p
    If you think you already have an Raids Per Loot account, and you were just trying to associate a new authentication with your existing account, then you’re in the wrong place. You’re not logged into Raids Per Loot right now.
  %p.small.nomargin
    If you have a Raids Per Loot account, and you’d like to associate another authentication with it, here’s what to do:
  %ul.small
    %li Log in in to Raids Per Loot with your existing authentication service
    %li Go to your settings page (next to the sign-in menu)
    %li Add one or more accounts to be used to sign-in
